<!-- Our Story Section -->
<section class="about-section" id="story" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Humble Beginnings</h2>
        <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570196917203-59f2c611a5b5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80"
                     alt="Ice Cream Making"
                     class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3 class="mb-4">A Family Passion Since 1985</h3>
                <p>Creamy Bar began as a small family-owned ice cream parlor in a quiet neighborhood. Founded by Maria and Giovanni Ricci, our story started with a single secret family recipe passed down through generations.</p>
                <p>What began as a weekend hobby quickly turned into a neighborhood favorite. The Ricci family's commitment to using only the freshest, highest-quality ingredients and their innovative approach to classic flavors soon gained a loyal following.</p>
                <p>Today, while we've grown to multiple locations across the country, we still make our ice cream the same way Maria and Giovanni did - with love, patience, and an uncompromising commitment to quality.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline -->
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-year">1985</div>
                    <h4>The First Scoop</h4>
                    <p>Maria and Giovanni Ricci open their first ice cream parlor with just 6 flavors. Their signature "Ricci's Dream" becomes an instant local favorite.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-year">1995</div>
                    <h4>First Expansion</h4>
                    <p>Due to overwhelming demand, Creamy Bar opens its second location. We introduce our first dairy-free options to accommodate more customers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2005</div>
                    <h4>National Recognition</h4>
                    <p>Creamy Bar wins "Best Artisanal Ice Cream" at the National Dessert Awards. We launch our first seasonal flavors collection.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2015</div>
                    <h4>Sustainability Commitment</h4>
                    <p>We commit to 100% sustainable sourcing and introduce compostable packaging. Our "Farm to Cone" program launches, partnering with local organic farms.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
                    <h4>Present Day</h4>
                    <p>With 25 locations nationwide and an online store shipping nationwide, Creamy Bar continues to innovate while staying true to our original family recipes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

